// Find peak kW value during on-peak hours (8am - 10pm )

import java.time.LocalDateTime
import java.time.LocalDate
import java.time.LocalTime
import java.time.format.DateTimeFormatter

val refTime = LocalTime.parse("08:00:00", DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("HH:mm:ss"))
txt.map(s=>s.split(",")).filter(s=> s(0).toInt == 26).filter(s=>LocalDateTime.parse(s(1), DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss") ).toLocalTime().isAfter(refTime)).filter(s=>LocalDateTime.parse(s(1), DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss") ).toLocalTime().isBefore(refTime.plusMinutes(480))   ).map(s=>s(2).toDouble).reduce((a,b)=>math.max(a,b))
